# oh-my-universal Skills for Cursor

You have access to 20 development skills from the oh-my-universal skills library.
Each skill is a structured workflow in `skills/{name}.md`. Read the skill file
when the user invokes it or when the situation calls for it.

## Quick Reference

| Trigger | Skill file | What it does |
|---------|-----------|-------------|
| "plan this" | skills/plan.md | Structured planning with self-critique |
| "review" | skills/review.md | High-signal code review (bugs/security only) |
| "ultrawork: {task}" | skills/ultrawork.md | Full lifecycle: plan→implement→verify→review→commit |
| "verify" | skills/verify.md | Evidence-based verification (supports diff-aware mode) |
| "security audit" | skills/security-review.md | Repo-wide security scan |
| "tdd: {feature}" | skills/tdd.md | Red → Green → Refactor |
| "fix build" | skills/build-fix.md | Auto-fix errors (3 attempts max) |
| "delegate" | skills/team.md | Split into parallel subtasks |
| "merge {repo}" | skills/repo-merge.md | External repo feature integration |
| "refactor" | skills/refactor.md | Improve structure, preserve behavior |
| "optimize" | skills/perf-audit.md | Performance profiling |
| "thorough review" | skills/multi-model-review.md | 4-perspective deep review |
| "doctor" | skills/doctor.md | Project health check |
| "map codebase" | skills/architecture.md | Understand structure |
| "update docs" | skills/doc-maintainer.md | Update affected docs |
| "remember" | skills/remember.md | Save learnings for future |
| "pre-commit" | skills/pre-commit-check.md | Quality gate before commit |
| "wrap up" | skills/session-protocol.md | End-of-session cleanup |
| "make skill" | skills/skillify.md | Create new skill from pattern |
| "notify" | skills/notify.md | Send completion notification |

## Proactive Use

- Before multi-file changes: read skills/plan.md
- Before committing: read skills/pre-commit-check.md
- After implementing: read skills/verify.md
- End of session: read skills/session-protocol.md
- When build fails: read skills/build-fix.md
